Package: eTRex
Type: Package
Title: epigenomics-based Transcriptional Regulator explorer
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-06-16
Author: Zeyu Lu
Maintainer: Zeyu Lu <zeyu.lu@uta.edu>
Description: Implements a variational Bayesian framework to infer transcriptional 
    regulator activity from ChIP-seqâ€“derived summaries. The package maps input 
    regions to genomic bins, aligns them to reference TR profiles, and produces 
    ranked regulators with uncertainty summaries and optional visualizations.
